title: Biocoop Element-Terre
description: A big warehouse wholefood and organic shop. Stocks many vegetarian and vegan products. Has tempeh, smoked tofu, oat-based vegan yoghurts as well as soya ones, a large range of fresh and packaged goods; plus household products and toiletries. It's up the hill on the other side of the Rance River to Dinan, a short way beyond the Intermarche supermarket.
streetAddress: Zone Cap Sud, rue Charles de Gaulle
